# Description: ace-prompt-prep getting started demonstration
# Tags: prompt, docs

Output ace-prompt-prep/docs/demo/ace-prompt-prep-setup-enhance.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 960
Set Height 540

Type "cd ace-prompt-prep"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "ace-prompt-prep setup"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "printf 'Review the critical path for this change.\n' > .ace-local/prompt-prep/prompts/the-prompt.md"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "ace-prompt-prep process --enhance"
Enter
Sleep 3s
